snippet.textDisplay: I am no expert, but I have seen planes in the sky and have seen surface to air missiles before. Both have different but noticeable light sources. The fact that we only see one light sorce is indicative of a plane that is roughly 5 miles away from this camera, The sound happens 25 seconds in which is about 5 seconds per mile. at 5 miles the planes anti-collision strobe lights may not be visible but the bright wing indication lights can be seen. That being said where is the trailing light from the rocket propellant that should be very visable even when filmed from a potato.:/ I dont know how this is being taken as conclusive evidence of missle attack. This could just as well be a bomb on board unrelated to iran, why would they want to take down a plane that was mostly full of Iranian-canadian citizens. Whose to say this wasnt an attack by the states to blame on iran. It just doesnt make sense
